Our limelight 3 is hooked up to a google coral right now, that I’m pretty sure works since we used it last season without issue.

Here’s what I’m seeing on the stream:

Im not sure what it means but we aren’t getting any detections so clearly something somewhere went wrong

I also don’t think the google coral is broken bcs I see it flashing a white light when hooked up and trying to run object detection.

I uploaded the detection tflite file meant for the coral (although I also tried CPU with little success as well), and it uploaded successfully, but is telling us to “check our runtime”.

Screenshot 2025-03-05 2023411310×388 26.9 KB

I tried switching between coral and cpu but still doesn’t work.

Any ideas?
